Less than 1 Flee for safety, hoping their opponents will tend to their disabled comrades instead of pursuing.
1  Flee in hopes of luring their opponents after them (possibly into a trap), then double back to seize their disabled opponents.
2  Kill the disabled opponents.
3 or 4   Whenever an opponent is paralyzed, pick them up and carry them off.
5 or 6   Ignore disabled opponents while there are other opponents left standing.
more than 6 Unless directly engaged in combat, kill disabled opponents, and spend the rest of the combat eating them.
